product_name: Asolo Outlaw Low GTX Hiking Shoes - Women's
long_description: Ideal for light hiking or everyday wear in wet weather, the lightweight, waterproof Asolo Outlaw Low GTX Hiking Shoes have a supportive and pleasant fit that mirrors the shape of your feet. Suede leather uppers have GORE-TEX(R) waterproof, breathable membranes that are guaranteed keep your feet dry on rainy days. The lower part of the last is anatomically shaped to cradle and support the feet; the heels are shaped to improve comfort. Vibram(R) soles have self-cleaning lugs designed for great performance on all types of terrain. Asolo Outlaw Low GTX Hiking Shoes have rubber toe caps for durability and protection.
